{"type":null,"faqId":19348,"title":"如何更改信息内容字体的大小？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>在信息界面，双指合拢滑动，或来开滑动，可以改变信息字体大小，不影响系统改字体。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>进入信息界面，打开选项菜单，点击</span><span class=\"s2\">设置</span><span>&gt;</span><span class=\"s2\">基本设置</span><span>&gt;</span><span class=\"s2\">信息文字大小</span><span>，选择需要显示的字体大小。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2489","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608223000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":7,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}